{"tid":321794,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"做左旅行社5年 你問我答","createTime":"2017-07-14T11:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T07:23:45.000Z","uid":85242,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6453012643a17d7d5b4b9ff4e63030d49104f5dc","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"隨便問 但唔會答做邊間"},{"pid":"678f8297dfa73233942ba133b6a8f2c415d91464","tid":321794,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:30:07.000Z","msg":"而家旅行社靠咩搵錢 仲有無得做<br />\n人工幾多？"},{"pid":"8b10796d49bac67cb289a4e0c9c60e04dfc76a65","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家旅行社靠咩搵錢 仲有無得做<br />\n人工幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗係靠現金收入再去投資 黎錢搵錢 。我覺得仲有得做 ，但競爭力講真真係大減，人工睇個人 同埋睇你做邊一範。我諗基本20k 到30k唔難"},{"pid":"875c0627e0886126839af51a32d66597dc162a46","tid":321794,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df7f09a32bb3fe09a4ab41878d7ee375100fc4b8","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做左十年，而家移民了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyo 咁有無轉行?"},{"pid":"3594d8cb386f1be2dbca6dc8f7837404c207e37e","tid":321794,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:23:30.000Z","msg":"大學畢業做領隊有無得諗？"},{"pid":"6789ec1a2d1d139dc298f3ee289184363c64ec62","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學畢業做領隊有無得諗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有得諗。領隊要肯涯 同埋預左比人插 。唔好諗住好快可以帶長線。但做耐左 真係搵到好多錢。<br />\n<br />\n識啲師兄。一年帶幾團已經搵夠 。但佢地講緊 30幾40"},{"pid":"681174bb8c6182634df67e6b4a612daa4507ba66","tid":321794,"uid":48980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"其實做領隊高唔高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa3b9b0d1d4828550d29df97591871b96075209","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實做領隊高唔高人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定有分淡旺季 。同埋真係好講經驗同埋有無熟客 <br />\n<br />\n只可以話唔穩定"},{"pid":"98702279cb1a092706fb100b6fba07b5dd8e1b60","tid":321794,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:47:58.000Z","msg":"大學畢業做左4個月想quit"},{"pid":"b806c1249179b45743d4405e2a050204cb16499a","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學畢業做左4個月想quit</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做邊範"},{"pid":"65e8bdef3c115cd64c554c0751eb72830dc8f51f","tid":321794,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"你地d酒店機票係邊個綱訂 都係大路個幾個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa74d69e810faa6b72a03accbe9b8743f4e22a2","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地d酒店機票係邊個綱訂 都係大路個幾個?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁一定唔係同普通啲人一樣咁上網訂 ，旅行社會有個系統睇到全世界的機票。酒店公司內部會有同當地旅行社聯絡訂房。<br />\n<br />\n其實你地上網訂機票酒店都係叫旅行社。只不過平台唔同，佢地唔係1對1咁服務 。佢地係著重方便 實惠。我地係著重服務，建議"},{"pid":"c01295de9dd885a93311ca2a99b9dbb0d312427c","tid":321794,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69f5185f558f41cb460ab764d4c2f9f693e4c4d","tid":321794,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"夕陽行業 俾d機票網酒店網打殘哂"},{"pid":"c21fbcb4756c77f086613289b78d93580a2bee9a","tid":321794,"uid":11980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有暗盤"},{"pid":"38d950023c437853c815381b66b0da1ee4504550","tid":321794,"uid":1983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:10:37.000Z","msg":"西歐係咪每團都咁多水魚買錶"},{"pid":"4ebb64ae8bb474c1aba69487682fa1ee765a8995","tid":321794,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:14:15.000Z","msg":"好難做..........D生意差到<br />\n俾HX打到謝"},{"pid":"0dc07f12c3f0911a105f42cc29d0fb3b6eaf61b8","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n有冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為其實機票有好多種fare。有時航空公司會比旅行社一啲平的fare而本身航空公司無 。想知多啲 我可以詳細解釋<br />\n<br />\nsor1999"},{"pid":"0282241c06a4d61e170ae2fe553314a41202b549","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夕陽行業 俾d機票網酒店網打殘哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係差好多 但遠睇黎講 我覺得仲有得做 始終網上平台以平價吸客 佢落咁多廣告 自然成本高"},{"pid":"20222a9a5edc61e290d8db1224136067aa0e57ff","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難做..........D生意差到<br />\n俾HX打到謝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHx真係堅 而家愈做愈多航線 價錢又平啲"},{"pid":"cd5fa9b2406f06a42548454c3c666f6561c86b9c","tid":321794,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"做緊領隊?<br />\n幾$一個月,除番每月平均<br />\n旅行社BACK OFFICE 經驗十幾年經驗既經理都係得2皮,會否太ON9"},{"pid":"772a8cbc8fd0cfeb401bf7c124cda0898e41dfe5","tid":321794,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有冇伏</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">暗盤</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CX GV package fare</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">價錢平左，限制自然多左</span><br />\n例如一定要二人同行<br />\nDate changed fee更貴，non refund等等<br />\n你唔改期，唔取消其實無影響"},{"pid":"f690ba01d4c5f1cbc37ee1f1f282c3d23b0fc77b","tid":321794,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有冇伏</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">暗盤</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CX GV package fare</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">價錢平左，限制自然多左</span><br />\n例如一定要二人同行<br />\nDate changed fee更貴，non refund等等<br />\n你唔改期，唔取消其實無影響</blockquote><br />\n最近睇到某旅行社既歐洲機票比航空公司平差唔多$1500<br />\n仲要係同一日出發 同一班機 考慮緊要唔要跟旅行社訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1169ca148ab9fe1686945aaf71f3dc2a89427353","tid":321794,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難做..........D生意差到<br />\n俾HX打到謝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHx真係堅 而家愈做愈多航線 價錢又平啲</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n係呀  屌佢 賣OKA  出個KA價 同個HX價<br />\nD客諗都唔撚諗KA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5ee5c7be1e3e052ab4e32b936522cc5fe13a52","tid":321794,"uid":96344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"大學grad有咩位可以做？<br />\nfront 定back office 好啲？"},{"pid":"ca4cd772034f8ecdcbb362eccffe9fceaecdffca","tid":321794,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解同一班機 經旅行社訂既機票比航空公司官網訂平咁多<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">有冇伏</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<span style=\"color: red;\">暗盤</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CX GV package fare</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">價錢平左，限制自然多左</span><br />\n例如一定要二人同行<br />\nDate changed fee更貴，non refund等等<br />\n你唔改期，唔取消其實無影響</blockquote><br />\n唔一定 普通飛都有<br />\n<br />\n但你記住機票呢d野越平個條款越嚴苛<br />\n<br />\n要留意返有d乜 例如唔俾改期 退款之類"},{"pid":"d14cfd5bb9a7c82817a7fee6822e07d76ee3b538","tid":321794,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"你地公司今年執左幾多間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a07131a1a480c17c93569838483528adc2aed1","tid":321794,"uid":85242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好難做..........D生意差到<br />\n俾HX打到謝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHx真係堅 而家愈做愈多航線 價錢又平啲</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n係呀  屌佢 賣OKA  出個KA價 同個HX價<br />\nD客諗都唔撚諗KA<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\noka呢條線 hx玩哂 時間贏哂"},{"pid":"94d0aa4c8febb958b31c3fed70fc8e420bb74dee","tid":321794,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T15:56:33.000Z","msg":"賣package係咪賺好少？"},{"pid":"9de6e2bc925d88b929e02fbf0659c3f673b14